data.text:
Find a clinic near you

For answers to your sexual health questions, counselling, testing and referrals, there are many sexual health clinics throughout Ontario that are here for you.

Find a sexual health clinic in your neighbourhood by visiting your public health unit’s website for more information. To find your public health unit, please visit ontario.ca/publichealth.

Find a PrEP clinic near you

PrEP is a highly effective way for some people to protect themselves from HIV and involves taking one pill a day. To talk to a health care provider about PrEP or to find a PrEP clinic close to you, please visit https://ontarioprep.ca/.

Find a clinic

Find a clinic near you for testing, treatment and counseling. Plus, learn more about the services your local clinic can offer you.

Let’s chat

Chat with us live for answers to your sexual health questions, information and assistance.

Monday – Friday: 10 am - 10:30 pm ET

Saturday & Sunday: 11 am - 3 pm ET

Statutory holidays: closed.
